Optimizing User Engagement Through A/B Testing: Data-Driven Insights

In this case study, I conducted an A/B test to analyze the impact of different call-to-action button texts on click-through rates. The results suggest a clear business implication: implementing this change could drive conversions and boost potential revenue.
